  <title>libva-intel-driver-&libva-intel-driver-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para> 
      This package contains the video decode and encode driver backend for the
      Intel G45 chipsets and Intel HD Graphics for Intel Core processor family.
    </para>

